org.sakaiproject.event.impl

Class BaseEventTrackingService.BaseEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.event.impl.BaseEventTrackingService.BaseEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.sakaiproject.event.api.Event
    Enclosing class:
    BaseEventTrackingService

    protected class BaseEventTrackingService.BaseEvent
extends Object
implements org.sakaiproject.event.api.Event, Serializable

    BaseEvent is the implementation of the Event interface.

    Event objects are posted to the EventTracking service, and may be listened for.
